item.title: Represented D'Hondt Thermal Solutions
item.description: Synergy Services began offering cooling tower erection and spare part replacement services and became a member of the Cooling Tower Institute (CTI) in Thailand. Additionally, we have been representing D’Hondt Thermal Solutions since 2010.
